### CREATE DIRECT CHAT
POST http://localhost:8000/chats/direct
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
}

### LIST CHATS
GET http://localhost:8000/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### GET CHAT DETAILS
GET http://localhost:8000/chats/{{chat_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### SEND MESSAGE
POST http://localhost:8000/chats/{{chat_id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Привет!"
}

### GET CHAT MESSAGES
GET http://localhost:8000/chats/{{chat_id}}/messages?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### MARK CHAT AS READ
POST http://localhost:8000/chats/{{chat_id}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
